ADVANCE: Raise your character level

Syntax: advance
        advance pick <stat>

When you have enough experience for the next level, advance raises your
character level manually. You are notified automatically when you cross
the threshold.

Each level-up grants:
  HP or MDC (depends on your body type and O.C.C.)
  PPE or ISP if your O.C.C. grants them
  +1 pending skill slot (spend with: improve <skill>)
  +1 life (protects against full death until lives reach 0)
  +1 APM at levels 3, 6, 9, 12, and 15

At even levels you may also pick a stat bonus:
  advance pick PS
  advance pick PP
  advance pick PE
  advance pick Spd

XP thresholds depend on your O.C.C. Check score for your current XP.

SEE ALSO: improve, levels, score
